    "In this survey paper, we have presented a comprehensive review of existing deep learningbased AES models.",
    "Our analysis delved into essay representation techniques, and various essay scoring models.",
    "Recognizing the importance of feedback in writing assessments, we also explored studies that focus on feedback identification and generation.",
    "Additionally, we discussed widely used AES datasets and evaluation metrics.",
    "It is worth noting that although many of the datasets used in AES research are not publicly available, it is possible to obtain access by establishing proper communication with the hosting organizations."
